    IATA RTP | CCAA in Yaoundé, Cameroon

    The CCAA Training School, established in 2016 offers multiple Aviation Safety and Security training programs. We are proud to provide multiple course options which gear towards candidates who wish to make a career out of their training. We are committed to use our expertise to provide candidates with quality training in a state-of-the-art environment.      

    The Training School has 2 centers, one in Yaoundé and another one in Douala.

    See the CCAA course schedule
